de.must.appletserver
Class AttributeList

java.lang.Object
  de.must.appletserver.AttributeList
All Implemented Interfaces:
InlayCenterContent
public class AttributeList
extends java.lang.Object
implements InlayCenterContent

Attribute list to layout components upon a panel line by line with a label at the beginning of each line. After an attribute list is completely filled, the labels may be packed according to the longest label via method packlabel. May be used e.g. to edit fields of a single database table record.
